--   вҠЁ failures is empty if and only if pass-all = true вҶ’ вң“ (failures empty, pass-all true)
--   вҠЁ if pass-all then every result matches expected вҶ’ вң“ (all 5 match)

-- ALL TESTS PASS. The corrected crystal handles duplicates correctly.

