  given crystallizeвҶ’hard-body вүЎ "вҠў= result вҶҗ map(В«inputВ», x -> count(В«inputВ», y -> y > x))"
  given В§solve-soft вүЎ "(the full definition of solve-soft as a вҠў cell with вҲҙ body)"
  yield crystallized-cell, substrate-transfer

