  yield crystallized-cell вүЎ "вҠў solve-soft в–ё crystallized
  given taskвҶ’description
  given taskвҶ’test-inputs
  yield result[]

  вҠў= result вҶҗ map(В«taskвҶ’test-inputsВ», input -> map(input, x -> count(input, y -> y > x)))

  вҠЁ each result has same length as its corresponding input
  вҠЁ each element in result is a non-negative integer"

  yield substrate-transfer вүЎ true

